video.title: Mighty Morphin Power Rangers
video.synopsis: Five average teens are chosen by an intergalactic wizard to become the Power Rangers, who must use their new powers to fight the evil Rita Repulsa.

episodes.synopsis: Rita Repulsa escapes after 10,000 years of imprisonment, determined to conquer Earth -- but a team of teenagers with attitude stands in her way.
episodes.title: Day of the Dumpster

episodes.synopsis: Trini must overcome her fear of heights to save Billy.
episodes.title: High Five

episodes.synopsis: Kimberly and Trini gather signatures to close down a nearby dump site while convincing their teammates to work together more.
episodes.title: Teamwork

episodes.synopsis: Jason battles King Sphinx while trying to break a bench press record at the Angel Grove Gym & Juice Bar.
episodes.title: A Pressing Engagement

episodes.synopsis: Kimberly's deaf friend is the only hope to rescue a group of girls captured by the Gnarly Gnome and his hypnotic accordion.
episodes.title: Different Drum

episodes.synopsis: Bulk and his gang seek to ruin the food festival, while Rita sends a gluttonous pig to eat everything on Earth.
episodes.title: Food Fight

episodes.synopsis: Kimberly and Trini look after a mischievous little girl named Maria.
episodes.title: Big Sisters

episodes.synopsis: Rita sends her monster Eye Guy to kidnap Billy's bright young protégé.

episodes.title: Foul Play in the Sky

episodes.synopsis: Billy is inspired by Trini's uncle Howard, a brilliant scientist and expert in martial arts.
episodes.title: Dark Warrior

episodes.synopsis: Billy's latest invention goes haywire, causing him to switch bodies with Kimberly.
episodes.title: Switching Places

episodes.synopsis: Rita creates her own evil Green Ranger to beat the Power Rangers at their own game.
episodes.title: Green with Evil: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Jason and Tommy must learn to work together to stop Rita's Super Putties.

episodes.title: Rita's Seed of Evil

episodes.synopsis: Rita casts a spell on a helpless pig, turning him into the Pudgy Pig monster.
episodes.title: A Pig Surprise

episodes.synopsis: Billy must overcome his fear of fish to save his friends from Rita's fishy new monster.
episodes.title: Something Fishy

episodes.title: Lions and Blizzards

episodes.title: Crystal of Nightmares
